oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ambrose Haley and his Ozark Ramblers performances
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various performances by Ambrose Haley and his Ozark Ramblers (performers) [according to tape case] on December 24 and February 4 from an unknown year.
